title: TICK-TOCK JELLY CLOCK COSMOTRON

thumbnail.alt_text: A work made of wall component: wood, fabric, cardboard, wallpaper, magazine pages, stickers, string, twine, plastic film, glass fragments, mirror fragments, iron straps, grommets, nails, screws, upholstery tacks, metal foil, aluminum sheet, electrical socket, electrical wiring, rubber hose, beads, costume jewelry parts, sequins, ribbon, nylon stocking, cigarette filter, paint, graphite, bitumen, and resin on pressed hardboard; painted wood frame with mirror segments. floor component: wood spool, fiberboard cone, paper, paint, monofilament netting, electrical plug, insulated wire, speaker, audio cable, iron wire, rings and clips, paper, yarn, and twine; 1/4 in. reel-to-reel audio tape transferred to digital format..

dimensions: Wall component: 146 × 136.5 × 12.7 cm (57 1/2 × 53 3/4 × 5 in.); cone: 111.1 × 38.1 cm diameter ×  (43 3/4 × 15 in. diameter)
